ossible\" \"In 1 month\" \"In 3 months\" \"More than 6 months\" \"Not sure / to be determined\"]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"callout secondary\">\n<div class=\"field\"><label for=\"description\"><strong>Project Description <span class=\"required\">*</span></strong></label></div>\n<p>Please briefly describe your project, what you aim to achieve, what you\'d like me to do, and link to any appropriate materials (such as PSDs available via Dropbox).</p>\n<div class=\"field\">[textarea* hdescription id:description rows:5 placeholder \"We need a brand new website and web apps development for our products. you can access our brief at this link: https://goo.gl/emBkzw\"]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fields\">[submit id:submit class:button class:large \"Send\"]</div>\n</fieldset>');
