Enter atau membuat baris baru, teks diatas akan langsung secara otomatis berubah menjadi format yang di inginkan.\r\n\r\nBeberapa kumpulan shortcut keyboard yang tersedia antara lain:\r\n\r\n<strong>*</strong> – Memulai unordered list\r\n<strong>–</strong> – Memulai unordered list\r\n<strong>1.</strong> – Memulai ordered list\r\n<strong>1)</strong> – Memulai unordered list\r\n<strong>##</strong> – H2\r\n<strong>###</strong> – H3\r\n<strong>####</strong> – H4\r\n<strong>#####</strong> – H5\r\n<strong>######</strong> – H6\r\n<strong>&gt;</strong> – Menambahkan blockquote\r\n<strong>—</strong> – Menambahkan horizontal line\r\n<strong>`..`</strong> – Merubah teks menjadi blok kode (ganti .. dengan teks anda)\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nPada bagian atas editor, terdapat 2 tab, Visual dan Text (<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3333 size-full\" title=\"Visual/Text\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/editor_visualtext.jpg\" alt=\"Visual/Text\" width=\"105\" height=\"28\" />). Tab ini akan mengganti tampilan editor antara Visual Editor dan Text Editor. Pada tampilan Text View anda dapat melihat kode HTML yang membentuk konten anda. Untuk pengguna yang lebih berpengalaman ini akan membantu, namun tidak sebaliknya pada pengguna yang kurang familiar dengan tag HTML.\r\n\r\nKetika membuat Page atau Post baru, hal pertama yang harus anda lakukan adalah mengisi Judul (Title) yang berada pada field paling atas dan terdapat teks bantu Enter title here. Setelah itu anda dapat secara bebas mengatur konten anda.\r\n\r\nPada bagian atas tempat konten anda ditulis, terdapat banyak tombol formatting, klik pada tombol Toolbar Toggle (<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3320 size-full\" title=\"Toolbar Toggle\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/editor_kitchensink.jpg\" alt=\"Toolbar Toggle\" width=\"26\" height=\"24\" />)  akan menampilkan atau menyembunyikan baris kedua dari tombol formatting yang akan memberi anda fungsionalitas tambahan. Tombol-tombol Editor berfungsi sebagai berikut:\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"158px\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3303 size-full\" title=\"Add Media\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/editor_addmedia.jpg\" alt=\"Add Media\" width=\"105\" height=\"28\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Add Media</strong> – Menambahkan media seperti gambar, suara, video atau dokumen.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3327 size-full\" title=\"Style\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/editor_style.jpg\" alt=\"Style\" width=\"107\" height=\"26\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Style</strong> – Digunakan untuk memberi format pada teks</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3309 size-full\" title=\"Bold\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/editor_bold.jpg\" alt=\"Bold\" width=\"26\" height=\"24\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Bold</strong> – Bold / Menebalkan teks</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3319 size-full\" title=\"Italic\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/editor_italic.jpg\" alt=\"Italic\" width=\"26\" height=\"24\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Italic</strong> – Italic / Memiringkan teks</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3332 size-full\" title=\"Bulleted List\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/editor_unorderedlist.jpg\" alt=\"Bulleted List\" width=\"26\" height=\"24\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Bulleted List</strong> – Membuat unordered (bullet point) list</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3321 size-full\" title=\"Numbererd List\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/editor_orderedlist.jpg\" alt=\"Numbererd List\" width=\"26\" height=\"24\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Numbered List</strong> – Membuat Ordered (numbered) list</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3308 size-full\" title=\"Blockquote\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/editor_blockquote.jpg\" alt=\"Blockquote\" width=\"26\" height=\"24\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Blockquote</strong> – Digunakan untuk menampilkan quote / kutipan.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3306 size-full\" title=\"Align Left\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/editor_alignleft.jpg\" alt=\"Align Left\" width=\"26\" height=\"24\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Align left</strong> – Membuat teks rata kiri</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3304 size-full\" title=\"Align Center\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/editor_aligncenter.jpg\" alt=\"Align Center\" width=\"26\" height=\"24\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Align Center</strong> – Membuat teks rata tengah</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3307 size-full\" title=\"Align Right\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/editor_alignright.jpg\" alt=\"Align Right\" width=\"26\" height=\"24\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Align Right</strong> – Membuat teks rata kanan</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3317 size-full\" title=\"Insert/edit Link\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/editor_insertlink.jpg\" alt=\"Insert/edit Link\" width=\"26\" height=\"24\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Insert/edit link</strong> – Digunakan untuk menambahkan link HTML untuk ke website lain atau link dari website kita sendiri.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3318 size-full\" title=\"Insert Read More tag\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/editor_insertmore.jpg\" alt=\"Insert Read More tag\" width=\"26\" height=\"24\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Insert Read More tag – </strong>Batas untuk deskripsi singkat dari artikel atau disebut dengan Excerpt pada sistem wordpress</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3320\" title=\"Toolbar Toggle\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/editor_kitchensink.jpg\" alt=\"Toolbar Toggle\" width=\"26\" height=\"24\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Toolbar Toggle</strong> – Digunakan untuk menampilkan baris kedua dari Toolbar</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3312 size-full\" title=\"Distraction Free Writing\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/editor_fullscreen.jpg\" alt=\"Distraction Free Writing\" width=\"26\" height=\"24\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Distraction Free Writing</strong> – Klik tombol ini akan mengekspan tampilan editor hingga memenuhi layar browser (Full Screen), anda akan lebih fokus dalam menulis. Klik tombol ini lagi untuk mengembalikan tampilan ke tampilan semula.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3326 size-full\" title=\"Strikethrough\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/editor_strikethrough.jpg\" alt=\"Strikethrough\" width=\"26\" height=\"24\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Strikethrough</strong> – Menambahkan strikethrough pada teks anda</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3314 size-full\" title=\"Horizontal Line\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/editor_horizontalline.jpg\" alt=\"Horizontal Line\" width=\"26\" height=\"24\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Horizontal Line</strong> – Menambahkan garis horizontal pada halaman anda</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3328 size-full\" title=\"Text Color\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/editor_textcolor.jpg\" alt=\"Text Color\" width=\"42\" height=\"24\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Text color</strong> – Merubah warna teks</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3323 size-full\" title=\"Paste as Text\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/editor_pastetext.jpg\" alt=\"Paste as Text\" width=\"26\" height=\"24\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Paste as Text</strong> – Paste sebagai teks, ini akan menghilangkan semua formatting yang terbawa saat anda melakukan copy dari sumber lainnya.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3325 size-full\" title=\"Clear Formatting\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/editor_removeformatting.jpg\" alt=\"Clear Formatting\" width=\"26\" height=\"24\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Clear formatting</strong> – Menghilangkan seluruh formatting dari teks yang di seleksi</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3316 size-full\" title=\"Special Character\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/editor_insertcharacter.jpg\" alt=\"Special Character\" width=\"26\" height=\"24\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Special character</strong> – Menambahkan karakter spesial, seperti simbol2 yang tidak bisa ditambahkan melalui keyboard</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3322 size-full\" title=\"Decrease Indent\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/editor_outdent.jpg\" alt=\"Decrease Indent\" width=\"26\" height=\"24\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Decrease indent</strong> – Mengurangi satu level indentasi</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3315 size-full\" title=\"Increase Indent\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/editor_indent.jpg\" alt=\"Increase Indent\" width=\"26\" height=\"24\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Increase Indent</strong> – Menambahkan satu level indentasi</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3330 size-full\" title=\"Undo\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/editor_undo.jpg\" alt=\"Undo\" width=\"26\" height=\"24\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Undo</strong> – Undo, mengulang aksi terakhir yang dilakukan</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3324 size-full\" title=\"Redo\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/editor_redo.jpg\" alt=\"Redo\" width=\"26\" height=\"24\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Redo</strong> – Redo, mengembalikan state ke aksi terakhir yang sempat di Undo</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3313 size-full\" title=\"Keyboard shortcuts\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/editor_help.jpg\" alt=\"Keyboard shortcuts\" width=\"26\" height=\"24\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Keyboard shortcuts</strong> – Menampilkan informasi mengenai Visual Editor WordPress beserta seluruh shortcutnya.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3333 size-full\" title=\"Visual/Text\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/editor_visualtext.jpg\" alt=\"Visual/Text\" width=\"105\" height=\"28\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Visual/Text</strong> – Mengganti tampilan editor antara Visual Editor dan Text Editor</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em>Terakhir di-update: Desember 2017</em>', 'Using Visual Editor', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '661-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-12-21 18:06:37', '2017-12-21 11:06:37', '', 661, 'https://www.ervandra.com/uncategorized/661-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
