(664, 1, '2017-12-21 22:10:59', '2017-12-21 15:10:59', '&nbsp;\r\n\r\nText Editor sama juga seperti Visual Editor, hanya saja tidak intuitif. Tombol formatting menyediakan anda dengan fungsi HTML dasar saat anda meng-edit konten Page atau Post.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBerikut adalah tombol editor yang tersedia pada mode Text Editor:\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"20%\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3338 size-full\" title=\"HTML Bold\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/html-edit_bold.jpg\" alt=\"HTML Bold\" width=\"26\" height=\"25\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"80%\"><strong>Bold</strong> – Bold teks</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3344 size-full\" title=\"HTML Italic\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/html-edit_italic.jpg\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"80%\"><strong>Italic</strong> – Italic / Memiringkan Teks</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3345 size-full\" title=\"HTML Edit Link\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/html-edit_link.jpg\" alt=\"HTML Edit Link\" width=\"30\" height=\"25\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Link</strong> – Digunakan untuk menambahkan link website lain atau website sendiri</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3337 size-full\" title=\"HTML Blockquote\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/html-edit_blockquote.jpg\" alt=\"HTML Blockquote\" width=\"54\" height=\"25\" /></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Blockquote</strong> – Digunakan untuk menampilkan quote / kutipan</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3341 size-full\" title=\"HTML Delete\" src=\"https://easywpguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/html-edit_