(270, 1, '2017-10-15 13:49:59', '2017-10-15 06:49:59', '<strong>Homer</strong> comes from the Greek meaning “<em>promise</em>”. Starting with the name, they continue to instill in them including all of their employees to be able to serve and provide the best for all their customers.\r\n\r\n<strong>Homer Interior</strong> believe that anything that starts from the values of the good it will bring good results as well. they doing business as Interior Fabrics Indonesia, is your one-stop shop decorative fabrics outlet store. They provide interior decorator with quality products, affordable prices, and excellent customer service.\r\n\r\nWhile they do specialize in fabrics of every color and texture, that’s not all they have to offer. They carry a wide selection of pillow forms, as well as custom furniture products such as sofa, chair, ottoman and headboard frames. Additionally, they have everything their customers need to create beautiful window treatments for their home, including tassels, hardware made of iron and wood. They are also proud to offer a quality window blinds such as roller blind, vertical blinds, roman shade, wood blind, etc.\r\n\r\nWhat makes them unique is that they avoid the middleman and skip excess mark-ups by buying directly from the mills. This allows their customers to buy quality products without paying astronomical prices. They also feel that their customers money should be spent on products, and products alone, which is why they appearance of their store remains humble, not flashy.\r\n\r\nAll items can be found in their retail store.\r\n<h5>HOMER Interior Web Design &amp; Development</h5>\r\n[gallery type=\"rectangular\" ids=\"271,272,273,274,275,276\"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nVisit project site: <a href=\"https://www.homer-interior.com\" title=\"https://www.homer-interior.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"button\" style=\"margin:0;\">https://www.homer-interior.com</a>', 'Homer Interior', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open',