(306, 1, '2017-10-15 14:33:30', '2017-10-15 07:33:30', 'When well production slows down sometimes it is not simply due to natural reservoir depletion. Sometimes it is because of downhole problems that happen in one or more wells. In order to fix the issues, the relevant possible cause(s) should be found in a time and cost-effective manner. Provided there are sufficient reserves to justify the cost, it is in the oil and gas operating companies’ best interest to rectify the issues.\r\n\r\n<strong>PT Iliadi Cipta Energi</strong> serve the industry by finding the issues of declining production that are not associated with natural reservoir depletion, making a case to justify the effort to fix the issues, elaborating the required action plans or technological solutions and promoting their participation in related execution tasks, ultimately in order to save production.\r\n<h5>Iliadi Web Design &amp; Development</h5>\r\n[gallery type=\"rectangular\" ids=\"299,300,301,302,303,304\"]', 'Iliadi', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '297-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-15 14:33:30', '2017-10-15 07:33:30', '', 297, 'https://www.ervandra.com/uncategorized/297-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
