(337, 1, '2017-10-15 20:24:43', '2017-10-15 13:24:43', 'The <strong>Innovative Formula</strong> Group started out in Kuala Lumpur in 2002 when Catherine de Padua and Lilian Beh decided to step out of the comfort zone of their corporate world to embrace their passion to help others live their best. Catherine and Lilian still hold to the philosophy that when people are engaged in their own learning, the experience becomes more thought-provoking, effective and most importantly, enjoyable.\r\n\r\nThey started out working from their homes with a firm belief that they could bring world-class leadership solutions with an Asian flavor to their clients. At that time, they had no idea that they would be blessed by wonderful network of facilitators who had both a wealth of experience, expertise and passion towards working with others to help them with their workplace issues.\r\n<h5>Innovative Formula Web Design &amp; Development</h5>\r\n[gallery type=\"rectangular\" ids=\"338,339,340\"]\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nVisit project site: <a href=\"https://innovative-formula.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://innovative-formula.com/</a>', 'Innovative Formula', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'innovative-formula', '', '', '2017-10-15 20:24:43', '2017-10-15 13:24:43', '', 0, 'https://www.ervandra.com/?p=337', 0, 'post', '', 0),
