(513, 1, '2017-11-01 10:16:18', '2017-11-01 03:16:18', 'I offer a one-stop <strong>Digital Marketing Solution</strong> that is tailored to the individual client to grasp the vast opportunities that your <strong>brand</strong> or <strong>business</strong> has in this growing digital age. I am focused on <strong>strategy</strong> and <strong>execution</strong> on consumer <strong>insight</strong>, <strong>modern technology</strong>, and boundless <strong>creativity</strong> across an integrated range of media.\r\n\r\nI have several teams that capable to solve all your digital-marketing solutions, from <strong>business consultancy</strong>, <strong>web design &amp; development</strong>, <strong>SEO optimization</strong>, <strong>email marketing</strong>, <strong>mobile apps development</strong>, to <strong>maintenance</strong> and <strong>content writing</strong>. Just right with all your business needs.', 'Services', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'services', '', '', '2017-11-01 16:33:04', '2017-11-01 09:33:04', '', 0, 'https://www.ervandra.com/?page_id=513', 2, 'page', '', 0),
(425, 1, '2017-10-22 21:00:29', '2017-10-22 14:00:29', '<strong>CIAYO</strong> is a <strong>virtual social media platform</strong>, they provides beautiful activity and item illustrations for user to share with friends. Combined with tech-in-edge attractive and interactive user experience scroll through their activity feeds.\r\n\r\nUser can posting their <strong>activity</strong>, <strong>mention</strong> their <strong>favorite</strong> <strong>items</strong>, <strong>favorite</strong> <strong>places</strong>, and <strong>tag</strong> their <strong>friends</strong>. Served well with <strong>commenting</strong> system, <strong>stickers</strong>, and <strong>reactions</strong>.\r\n\r\nIn-app <strong>Store</strong> also available, users can <strong>buy</strong> <strong>stickers</strong>, <strong>activities</strong>, <strong>emojis</strong>, <strong>merchandises</strong>, and many more. They can collect <strong>Caps</strong> and <strong>Cans</strong> which is in-app-currency.\r\n<h5>CIAYO Front-End Integration</h5>\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_427\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"1024\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-427\" src=\"https://www.ervandra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ciayo-virsos-1.jpg\" alt=\"CIAYO Virtual Social Media\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" /> CIAYO Timeline Card[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_428\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"1024\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-428\" src=\"https://www.ervandra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ciayo-virsos-2.jpg\" alt=\"CIAYO Virtual Social Media\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" /> CIAYO Timeline Scroll[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_429\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"1024\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-429\" src=\"https://www.ervandra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ciayo-virsos-3.jpg\" alt=\"CIAYO Virtual Social Media\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" /> CIAYO User Profile[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_430\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"1024\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-430\" src=\"https://www.ervandra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ciayo-virsos-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" /> CIAYO Store[/caption]\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h5>CIAYO Mobile Layout</h5>\r\n[gallery type=\"rectangular\" ids=\"431,432,433\"]\r\n\r\n[gallery type=\"rectangular\" ids=\"434,435\"]\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3>Requirements</h3>\r\nIn CIAYO we need an <strong>comprehensive</strong> yet <strong>modern</strong> <strong>web technologies</strong> that can <strong>accommodate</strong> our user needs. Integrated with a <strong>hassle-free</strong> <strong>backend</strong> and <strong>server</strong> <strong>architectures</strong>.\r\n<h3>Architectures</h3>\r\nWe absolutely need a <strong>blazing fast web apps</strong>, that\'s why we using <strong>Angular JS</strong>, which is a <strong>Single Page Application</strong> (SPA) framework from <strong>Google.</strong> Back in time, this <strong>Javascript Framework</strong> (AngularJs) is the best available in the market.\r\n<h3>Results</h3>\r\nBeing in teamwork with <strong>7 awesome Front-End Developers</strong>:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Donny Riantori</strong> (Front-End Leader) <a title=\"https://www.facebook.com/driantori\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/driantori\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><small style=\"display: none;\">View profile:</small><span class=\"fa fa-facebook-square\"> </span></a></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Ervandra Halim</strong> (Front-End Senior) <a title=\"https://www.facebook.com/vahnisme\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/vahnisme\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><small style=\"display: none;\">View profile:</small><span class=\"fa fa-facebook-square\"> </span></a></li>\r\n 	<li>H<strong>endra Kurniawan</strong> (Front-End Developer) <a title=\"https://www.facebook.com/themcmxciv\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/themcmxciv\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><small style=\"display: none;\">View profile:</small><span class=\"fa fa-facebook-square\"> </span></a></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Daniel Guitara</strong> (Front-End Developer) <a title=\"https://www.facebook.com/mdanielguitara\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mdanielguitara\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><small style=\"display: none;\">View profile:</small><span class=\"fa fa-facebook-square\"> </span></a></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Ferry Feriawan</strong> (Front-End Developer) <a title=\"https://www.facebook.com/feirone\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/feirone\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><small style=\"display: none;\">View profile:</small><span class=\"fa fa-facebook-square\"> </span></a></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Ari Sunarya</strong> (Front-End Developer) <a title=\"https://www.facebook.com/thulank.jr\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/thulank.jr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><small style=\"display: none;\">View profile:</small><span class=\"fa fa-facebook-square\"> </span></a></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Sandy Cahya</strong> (Front-End Developer) <a title=\"https://www.facebook.com/sandycahya23\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sandycahya23\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><small style=\"display: none;\">View profile:</small><span class=\"fa fa-facebook-square\"> </span></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe finally launched <strong>CIAYO Virtual Social Media Platform</strong> in <strong>Popcon Asia 2016</strong>. Reach about <strong>13K</strong> <strong>registered users</strong> in <strong>2 months</strong>.\r\n<h3>User-demand</h3>\r\nOur company (<strong>startup</strong>) is very considerable and listen to our user voices and needs, that\'s why we choose to pivoting our business and products. Later we launched <strong>CIAYO Comics</strong> as a result of this action.', 'CIAYO', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ciayo', '', '', '2017-10-23 08:15:21', '2017-10-23 01:15:21', '', 0, 'https://www.ervandra.com/?p=425', 0, 'post', '', 0),
