(482, 1, '2017-10-22 18:25:30', '2017-10-22 11:25:30', '<strong>CIAYO Blog</strong> makes it easy to keep up with the constant update of <strong>pop</strong> <strong>culture</strong> <strong>news</strong>. Pop culture has become such a <strong>phenomenon</strong> in <strong>Indonesia</strong> yet we currently have very few credible news outlets who focus on pop cultures. Pop culture doesn’t have to be misunderstood and underestimated—pop culture can be a powerful tool to bring people together.\r\n\r\nWe understood that birds of the same feathers flock together, and so we would like to gather all like-minded people in to the discussion of what they love the most. CIAYO Blog is all about connecting people with the same interests and ideas in their mind, and enhancing them up to eleven by facts and up-to-date news.\r\n\r\nThis is our creed: <strong>to share our passion and joy, and to make the world a better place by doing something that we love</strong>. As the old adage goes, do what you love and love what you do\r\n<h5>CIAYO Blog Web Design &amp; Development</h5>\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_461\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"895\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-461\" src=\"https://www.ervandra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ciayo-blog-1.jpg\" alt=\"CIAYO Blog\" width=\"895\" height=\"600\" /> CIAYO Blog Homepage[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_466\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"895\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-466\" src=\"https://www.ervandra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ciayo-blog-6.jpg\" alt=\"CIAYO Blog\" width=\"895\" height=\"600\" /> CIAYO Stories Challenge: Winner[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_465\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"895\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-465\" src=\"https://www.ervandra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ciayo-blog-5.jpg\" alt=\"CIAYO Blog\" width=\"895\" height=\"600\" /> CIAYO Stories Challenge[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_464\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"895\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-464\" src=\"https://www.ervandra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ciayo-blog-4.jpg\" alt=\"CIAYO Blog\" width=\"895\" height=\"600\" /> CIAYO Blog Article Bottom Section[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_463\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"895\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-463\" src=\"https://www.ervandra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ciayo-blog-3.jpg\" alt=\"CIAYO Blog\" width=\"895\" height=\"600\" /> CIAYO Blog Article Detail[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_462\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"895\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-462\" src=\"https://www.ervandra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ciayo-blog-2.jpg\" alt=\"CIAYO Blog\" width=\"895\" height=\"600\" /> CIAYO Blog Latest Articles[/caption]\r\n\r\n<hr/>\r\n<h5>Mobile Web</h5>\r\n[gallery type=\"rectangular\" ids=\"467,468,469,470,471\"]\r\n<hr/>\r\n<h3>Requirements</h3>\r\n<strong>CIAYO Corp</strong> need a <strong>powerful</strong> and <strong>hassle-free CMS</strong> for our editorial staffs. We need a <strong>blog</strong> to promote and bring <strong>brand awareness</strong> for <strong>CIAYO Corp</strong>, <strong>CIAYO Comics</strong>, and <strong>CIAYO Games</strong>, as well as share a lot of news about pop culture, games, comics, and anything else.\r\n<h3>Results</h3>\r\nThis <strong>masterpiece</strong> getting done with <strong>1 Front-End Developer</strong>, and a <strong>great-detailed-pixel-perfect</strong> <strong>Web Designer</strong>:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Ervandra Halim</strong> (Full Stack Developer) <a title=\"https://www.facebook.com/vahnisme\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/vahnisme\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><small style=\"display: none;\">View profile:</small><span class=\"fa fa-facebook-square\">&nbsp;</span></a></li>\r\n<li><strong>Kuncoro Jatikusumo</strong> (UI Designer) <a title=\"https://www.facebook.com/choro.jk\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/choro.jk\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><small style=\"display: none;\">View profile:</small><span class=\"fa fa-facebook-square\">&nbsp;</span></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr/>\r\nVisit CIAYO Blog: <a href=\"https://blog.ciayo.com\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"button hollow medium\" style=\"margin:0\">https://blog.ciayo.com</a>', 'CIAYO Blog', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '459-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-22 18:25:30', '2017-10-22 11:25:30', '', 459, 'https://www.ervandra.com/uncategorized/459-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(458, 1, '2017-10-22 17:49:30', '2017-10-22 10:49:30', '<strong>CIAYO</strong> is a <strong>virtual social media platform</strong>, they provides beautiful activity and item illustrations for user to share with friends. Combined with tech-in-edge attractive and interactive user experience scroll through their activity feeds.\r\n\r\nUser can posting their <strong>activity</strong>, <strong>mention</strong> their <strong>favorite</strong> <strong>items</strong>, <strong>favorite</strong> <strong>places</strong>, and <strong>tag</strong> their <strong>friends</strong>. Served well with <strong>commenting</strong> system, <strong>stickers</strong>, and <strong>reactions</strong>.\r\n\r\nIn-app <strong>Store</strong> also available, users can <strong>buy</strong> <strong>stickers</strong>, <strong>activities</strong>, <strong>emojis</strong>, <strong>merchandises</strong>, and many more. They can collect <strong>Caps</strong> and <strong>Cans</strong> which is in-app-currency.\r\n<h5>CIAYO Front-End Integration</h5>\r\n[gallery type=\"rectangular\" ids=\"427\"]\r\n\r\n[gallery type=\"rectangular\" ids=\"428\"]\r\n\r\n[gallery type=\"rectangular\" ids=\"429\"]\r\n\r\n[gallery type=\"rectangular\" ids=\"430\"]\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h5>CIAYO Mobile Layout</h5>\r\n[gallery type=\"rectangular\" ids=\"431\"]\r\n\r\n[gallery type=\"rectangular\" ids=\"432,433\"]\r\n\r\n[gallery type=\"rectangular\" ids=\"434,435\"]\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3>Requirements</h3>\r\nIn CIAYO we need an <strong>comprehensive</strong> yet <strong>modern</strong> <strong>web technologies</strong> that can <strong>accommodate</strong> our user needs. Integrated with a <strong>hassle-free</strong> <strong>backend</strong> and <strong>server</strong> <strong>architectures</strong>.\r\n<h3>Architectures</h3>\r\nWe absolutely need a <strong>blazing fast web apps</strong>, that\'s why we using <strong>Angular JS</strong>, which is a <strong>Single Page Application</strong> (SPA) framework from <strong>Google.</strong> Back in time, this <strong>Javascript Framework</strong> (AngularJs) is the best available in the market.\r\n<h3>Results</h3>\r\nBeing in teamwork with <strong>7 awesome Front-End Developers</strong>:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Donny Riantori</strong> (Front-End Leader) <a title=\"https://www.facebook.com/driantori\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/driantori\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><small style=\"display: none;\">View profile:</small> </a></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Ervandra Halim</strong> (Front-End Senior) <a title=\"https://www.facebook.com/vahnisme\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/vahnisme\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><small style=\"display: none;\">View profile:</small> </a></li>\r\n 	<li>H<strong>endra Kurniawan</strong> (Front-End Developer) <a title=\"https://www.facebook.com/themcmxciv\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/themcmxciv\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><small style=\"display: none;\">View profile:</small> </a></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Daniel Guitara</strong> (Front-End Developer) <a title=\"https://www.facebook.com/mdanielguitara\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mdanielguitara\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><small style=\"display: none;\">View profile:</small> </a></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Ferry Feriawan</strong> (Front-End Developer) <a title=\"https://www.facebook.com/feirone\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/feirone\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><small style=\"display: none;\">View profile:</small> </a></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Ari Sunarya</strong> (Front-End Developer) <a title=\"https://www.facebook.com/thulank.jr\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/thulank.jr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><small style=\"display: none;\">View profile:</small> </a></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Sandy Cahya</strong> (Front-End Developer) <a title=\"https://www.facebook.com/sandycahya23\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sandycahya23\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><small style=\"display: none;\">View profile:</small> </a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe finally launched <strong>CIAYO Virtual Social Media Platform</strong> in <strong>Popcon Asia 2016</strong>. Reach about <strong>13K</strong> <strong>registered users</strong> in <strong>2 months</strong>.\r\n<h3>User-demand</h3>\r\nOur company (<strong>startup</strong>) is very considerable and listen to our user voices and needs, that\'s why we choose to pivoting our business and products. Later we launched <strong>CIAYO Comics</strong> as a result of this action.', 'CIAYO', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '425-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-22 17:49:30', '2017-10-22 10:49:30', '', 425, 'https://www.ervandra.com/uncategorized/425-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
