(475, 1, '2017-10-23 18:15:14', '2017-10-23 11:15:14', '<strong>CIAYO Comics</strong> is, essentially, a sustainable ecosystem—a venue to nurture the relationship between <strong>authors</strong> and <strong>readers</strong>, so that a <strong>collaborative</strong> <strong>community</strong> is formed.\r\n\r\nCIAYO Comics is intended to <strong>eliminate</strong> the <strong>boundaries</strong> between readers and authors. We’re making <strong>reading comics</strong> an <strong>experience</strong> you won’t forget. It’s like a comic <strong>convention</strong>, but a <strong>personalized</strong> one.\r\n\r\nThat’s right. Now you can meet and greet any author you love right at your fingertips. Isn’t that nice?\r\n<h5>CIAYO Comics Front-End Development</h5>\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_489\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"1280\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-489\" src=\"https://www.ervandra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ciayo-comics-1.jpg\" alt=\"CIAYO Comics\" width=\"1280\" height=\"858\" /> CIAYO Comics: Home[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_490\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"1280\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-490\" src=\"https://www.ervandra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ciayo-comics-2.jpg\" alt=\"CIAYO Comics\" width=\"1280\" height=\"858\" /> CIAYO Comics: One-Shot Challenge[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_491\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"1280\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-491\" src=\"https://www.ervandra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ciayo-comics-3.jpg\" alt=\"CIAYO Comics\" width=\"1280\" height=\"858\" /> CIAYO Comics: Comic Chapters[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_492\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"1280\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-492\" src=\"https://www.ervandra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ciayo-comics-4.jpg\" alt=\"CIAYO Comics\" width=\"1280\" height=\"858\" /> CIAYO Comics: Comments[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_493\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"1280\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-493\" src=\"https://www.ervandra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ciayo-comics-5.jpg\" alt=\"CIAYO Comics\" width=\"1280\" height=\"858\" /> CIAYO Comics: User Profile[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_494\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"1280\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-494\" src=\"https://www.ervandra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ciayo-comics-6.jpg\" alt=\"CIAYO Comics\" width=\"1280\" height=\"858\" /> CIAYO Comics: One-Shot Challenge-Nominees[/caption]\r\n\r\n<hr/>\r\n<h5>Mobile Web apps</h5>\r\n[gallery type=\"rectangular\" ids=\"495,496,497\"]\r\n[gallery type=\"rectangular\" ids=\"498,499,500\"]\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3>Requirements</h3>\r\nWe need to built a very <strong>robust</strong> and <strong>comprehensive</strong> platform for our users, we will have a very <strong>high traffic</strong> and <strong>data flow</strong>, so we should estimate every detail for our <strong>client-server architectures</strong>.\r\n<h3>Architectures</h3>\r\nMy team decided to use React.js as a <strong>SPA</strong> Javascript Framework to build our comics platform. This framework is the best available at the market on the last-quarter of 2016.\r\n<h3>Results</h3>\r\nAs a result, we bring a whole new web apps experience for our users. A lot saying that they feels like they\'re using mobile application, but they are not. Thanks to SPA and our developer\'s hard-work, we are able to bring an <strong>even better comic reading experiences</strong>.\r\n\r\nSo many people involved in this projects, but we have <strong>4 very awesome Front-End Developer</strong> for this one:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Ervandra Halim</strong> (Front-End Project Leader) <a title=\"https://www.facebook.com/vahnisme\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/vahnisme\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><small style=\"display: none;\">View profile:</small><span class=\"fa fa-facebook-square\"> </span></a></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Hadianto Code Candy</strong> (Front-End Senior - Logic) <a title=\"https://www.facebook.com/hdicode\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hdicode\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><small style=\"display: none;\">View profile:</small><span class=\"fa fa-facebook-square\"> </span></a></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Ari Sunarya</strong> (Front-End Senior - Style) <a title=\"https://www.facebook.com/thulank.jr\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/thulank.jr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><small style=\"display: none;\">View profile:</small><span class=\"fa fa-facebook-square\"> </span></a></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Sandy Cahya</strong> (Front-End Senior - Logic) <a title=\"https://www.facebook.com/sandycahya23\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sandycahya23\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><small style=\"display: none;\">View profile:</small><span class=\"fa fa-facebook-square\"> </span></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nVisit CIAYO Comics: <a class=\"button alert large\" style=\"margin: 0; color:#fff\" href=\"https://www.ciayo.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://www.ciayo.com</a>', 'CIAYO Comics', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ciayo-comics', '', '', '2017-10-23 18:09:36', '2017-10-23 11:09:36', '', 0, 'https://www.ervandra.com/?p=475', 0, 'post', '', 0),
