(517, 1, '2017-11-01 16:31:37', '2017-11-01 09:31:37', 'My service operates like a start-up when it comes to web design and development. I can work in small teams and everyone does what they’re good at. My web design will work with/without graphic team to create a professional looking website and utilize multiple technologies (HTML5, CSS3, JQuery, etc) suitable for the project in order to achieve the best results.\r\n<h3>Web design with your audience in mind</h3>\r\nI create websites with intelligent architecture so it’s easy for your audience to find what they’re looking for, and i use analytics information tools to learn more about visitors’ behavior and create a positive experience that really engages your audience. I put a lot of thought into planning how your website is designed and structured so that visitors will understand your message in only a few seconds, and then find the information they are looking for in a few simple clicks.\r\n<h3>I know all about Responsive Design</h3>\r\nUsing Responsive Web Design (RWD) technique, i can also design your website so that the layouts can adapt to different viewing environments. This way, users across a broad range of devices (laptop, big screen monitors, iPhone, iPad, Galaxy tab, etc.) will have user-friendly navigation experience and easy to read content without compromising the look and feel of your website.\r\n<h3>Web design using industry best practice</h3>\r\nBuilding websites that will compete with the best in your industry really is a specialized skill, and not one you can give to inexperienced freelancer. I and my team live and breathe this type of work and take great pride in creating websites that are intuitive and engaging.\r\n<h3>I design website with SEO in mind</h3>\r\nAs a full service digital marketing freelancer, i also ensure that our websites are built in a way that maximizes their search engine rankings in Google, Yahoo! and Bing for products or services that clients offer.\r\n<h3>I integrate websites with powerful CMS</h3>\r\nI can integrate all websites that i build using an open-source, simple to use yet powerful Content Management System. I understand that in the future you may want to update your website on your own. Therefore with a very simple editing tool, you can edit your web pages similar to updating MS Word documents.', 'Web Design & Development', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'web-design-and-development', '', '', '2017-11-01 16:31:37', '2017-11-01 09:31:37', '', 513, 'https://www.ervandra.com/?page_id=517', 1, 'page', '', 0),
