(676, 1, '2017-12-22 11:19:05', '2017-12-22 04:19:05', 'Ketika anda meng-edit Post atau Page, terdapat jumlah revisi pada Post atau Page tersebut pada Publish panel.\r\n\r\nKlik Browse, maka anda akan melihat berbagai revisi yang anda lakukan pada Post atau Page.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-673\" src=\"https://www.ervandra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/posts-revisions.jpg\" alt=\"Posts Revisions\" width=\"1200\" height=\"400\" />\r\n\r\nGunakan slider yang terdapat pada bagian atas halaman, atau klik Previous dan Next untuk menavigasi melewati berbagai revisi Post dan Page.\r\n\r\nKonten yang telah terhapus akan ditandai dengan warna blok merah, dan yang ditambahkan akan ditandai dengan warna hijau.\r\n\r\nAnda juga dapat melakukan komparasi 2 revisi berbeda dengan klik Compare any two revisions pada bagian atas halaman.\r\n\r\nJika anda ingin restore revisi sebelumnya, klik tombol Restore This Revision.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-674\" src=\"https://www.ervandra.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/posts-revisions-review.jpg\" alt=\"Posts Revision Review\" width=\"1200\" height=\"695\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em>Terakhir di-update: Desember 2017</em>', 'Reviewing Past Version', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '672-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-12-22 11:19:05', '2017-12-22 04:19:05', '', 672, 'https://www.ervandra.com/uncategorized/672-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(759, 1, '2018-11-02 07:53:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Creating <strong>Editor\'s Choices</strong> component was not easy as it seems. There are a lot happening under the hood, so let\'s break down some things:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Prepare skeleton screen</li>\r\n 	<li>Create Component</li>\r\n 	<li>Fetch &amp; Render the Data</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Prepare Skeleton Screen</h3>\r\nWe need a skeleton screen to display pre-fetching layout, with a simple and little animation gimmick!\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_767\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"600\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-767\" src=\"https://www.ervandra.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/skeleton-editor-choice.jpg\" alt=\"skeleton-editor-choice\" width=\"600\" height=\"198\" /> Skeleton of Editor\'s Choices[/caption]\r\n\r\nCreate The Component\r\n\r\nWe\'re using containers and stateless component for this one\r\n<pre class=\"line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">class EditorsChoices extends Component {\r\n  state = {\r\n    isLoading: true,\r\n    isError: false,\r\n    editorsChoicesData: null,\r\n  };\r\n\r\n  getEditorsChoices = async _lang =&gt; {\r\n    this.setState({ isLoading: true, editorsChoicesData: null });\r\n    Axios.get(\r\n      `${process.env.API_ENDPOINT}comics/editor-choice?app=${\r\n        isMobile ? \'mobile\' : \'desktop\'\r\n      }&amp;language=${_lang}&amp;with=image,genres`,\r\n      { headers: { Authorization: `Bearer ${getUserToken()}` } }\r\n    )\r\n      .then(response =&gt; {\r\n        this.setState({\r\n          editorsChoicesData: response.data.c.data,\r\n        });\r\n      })\r\n      .catch(err =&gt; {\r\n        console.log(err);\r\n        this.setState({\r\n          isError: true,\r\n        });\r\n      })\r\n      .finally(() =&gt; {\r\n        this.setState({\r\n          isLoading: false,\r\n        });\r\n      });\r\n  };\r\n\r\n  componentDidMount = () =&gt; {\r\n    const { router } = this.props;\r\n    this.getEditorsChoices(router.query._lang);\r\n  };\r\n\r\n  render() {\r\n    const { isLoading, editorsChoicesData, isError } = this.state;\r\n    const { router } = this.props;\r\n\r\n    return (\r\n      &lt;EditorsChoicesStyle&gt;\r\n        &lt;div className=\"grid-container\"&gt;\r\n          &lt;div className=\"grid-x grid-margin-x\"&gt;\r\n            &lt;div className=\"cell\"&gt;\r\n              &lt;h3&gt;Editor\'s Choices&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n              &lt;div className=\"editor-choice-wrapper\"&gt;\r\n                {isLoading || !editorsChoicesData || isError ? (\r\n                  &lt;SkeletonLoading /&gt;\r\n                ) : (\r\n                  &lt;div className=\"editor-choice-carousel\"&gt;\r\n                    {editorsChoicesData.map(choice =&gt; (\r\n                      &lt;div className=\"editor-choice-item\" key={choice.code}&gt;\r\n                        &lt;EditorChoice\r\n                          data={choice}\r\n                          _lang={router.query._lang}\r\n                        /&gt;\r\n                      &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                    ))}\r\n                  &lt;/div&gt;\r\n                )}\r\n              &lt;/div&gt;\r\n            &lt;/div&gt;\r\n          &lt;/div&gt;\r\n        &lt;/div&gt;\r\n      &lt;/EditorsChoicesStyle&gt;\r\n    );\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\nEditorsChoices.propTypes = {\r\n  router: PropTypes.object.isRequired,\r\n};\r\n\r\nexport default withRouter(EditorsChoices);</code></pre>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAnd for the stateless as shown below', 'Remake Editor\'s Choice Component', '', 'draft', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2018-11-02 07:53:13', '2018-11-02 00:53:13', '', 0, 'https://www.ervandra.com/?p=759', 0, 'post', '', 0),
