(734, 1, '2018-09-05 14:55:33', '2018-09-05 07:55:33', '<strong>PAOL Promotions</strong> is, a portal website that offer custom-made bags with huge quantity available to deliver.\r\n\r\nWhy you should use PAOL Promotions service?\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><em>Fast Shipping</em></li>\r\n 	<li><em>99% satisfication rating</em></li>\r\n 	<li><em>25+ years total experience</em></li>\r\n 	<li><em>100% privacy guarantee</em></li>\r\n 	<li><em>50.000++ item shipped</em></li>\r\n 	<li>Personalized bags for all occasions!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThis website created using WordPress with hand-crafted Theme, make sure the website running as light and fast as possible by removing unnecessary plugins and bloating dependencies.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_739\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"600\"]<img class=\"size-large wp-image-739\" src=\"https://www.ervandra.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/paolpromotions-home-1200x900.jpg\" alt=\"Homepage of PAOL Promotions\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" /> Homepage of PAOL Promotions[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_738\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"600\"]<img class=\"size-large wp-image-738\" src=\"https://www.ervandra.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/paolpromotions-core-value-1200x900.jpg\" alt=\"Core Value of PAOL Promotions\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" /> Core Value of PAOL Promotions[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_737\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"600\"]<img class=\"size-large wp-image-737\" src=\"https://www.ervandra.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/paolpromotions-footer-1200x900.jpg\" alt=\"Footer of PAOL Promotions\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" /> Footer of PAOL Promotions[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_740\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"600\"]<img class=\"size-large wp-image-740\" src=\"https://www.ervandra.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/paolpromotions-contact-us-1200x900.jpg\" alt=\"Contact Us page of PAOL Promotions\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" /> Contact Us page of PAOL Promotions[/caption]\r\